OL,3,C'Inequitable' mooring charges
OL,4,Cprotested by Guernsey boatowners
OL,6,FIt is a culmination of months of
OL,7,Fcampaigning from Guernsey's
OL,8,Fboatowners, yacht clubs, and trade
OL,9,Fassociations.
OL,11,FTheir work has already encouraged the
OL,12,FStates' Trading Supervisory Board
OL,13,F(STSB) to reduce their proposed
OL,14,Fincreases for 2025 from an average of
OL,15,F25% to 8.3%.
OL,17,FThe STSB has yet to propose a figure
OL,18,Ffor 2026; however, they have
OL,19,Frecommended a "similarly modest"
OL,20,Fincrease, but boatowners are still
OL,21,Funsatisfied.
