OL,3,C'Inequitable' mooring charges
OL,4,Cprotested by Guernsey boatowners
OL,6,FThe group of boatowners have handed
OL,7,Ftheir petition to Deputy Peter Roffey,
OL,8,FPresident of the STSB, today (11
OL,9,FDecember 2024).
OL,11,FThe mooring charges regulations will
OL,12,Fbe debated in the States this week.
